"       <b>",
"        Growth Failure",
"       </b>",
"       contributes almost 7 points",
"to the PELD score.",
"      </li>",
"      <li>",
"       The",
"       <b>",
"        Listing Age Factor",
"       </b>",
"       term will be set to 0.436 if the subject is under 1 year of age, or if the",
"subject is less than 2 years old AND was listed before the age of 1 year.",
"      </li>",
"      <li>",
"       <b>",
"        Exception Diagnoses:",
"       </b>",
"       UNOS specifies urea cycle disorders, organic acidemia and hepatoblastoma",
"as exceptions to the PELD score calculation (and MELD score in patients between 12 and 17 years old).",
